<entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5088541708480462022</id><published>2020-03-06T20:45:44.622+08:00</published><updated>2020-03-06T20:45:44.622+08:00</updated><title type='text'>亮点在第3个问题，还有意说明是个小小的问题，反而是个大问题。想让博主经常在线，给六扇门抓住？&#xa;&#xa;很抱...</title><content type='html'>亮点在第3个问题，还有意说明是个小小的问题，反而是个大问题。想让博主经常在线，给六扇门抓住？&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;很抱歉，博主，虽然文不对题但这里人少，我就在这儿问了：&lt;br /&gt;1、如何看待维基解密披露的vault7项目？（刚出厂的苹果设备固件就已经带上了CIA的恶意软件）&lt;br /&gt;2、如果其它设备固件也中了类似“7号仓库”的招，如何尽可能躲避它们的监视？（没有理由认为天朝朝廷不会这么干）&lt;br /&gt;3、一个小小的问题，博主在Tor里有IRC频道吗？是否方便透露？&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/IRC</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/5088541708480462022'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/5088541708480462022'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1583498744622#c5088541708480462022' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2020年3月6日 下午8:45:00"/></entry>
